<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to DineDock</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* CSS Khusus Landing Page */
        body { background-color: #111; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* 1. HERO SECTION - Update Nama File Gambar Disini */
        .landing-hero {
            height: 90vh;
            /* Menggunakan 'restaurant.jpg' */
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), #111), url('/img/restaurant.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* 2. SHOWCASE SECTION */
        .showcase {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .showcase-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: #222;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .showcase-item:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); border-color: var(--gold); }
        .showcase-img { width: 100%; height: 250px; object-fit: cover; }
        .showcase-text { padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .showcase h3 { color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; }
        .showcase p { color: #aaa; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }

        /* 3. FOOTER */
        footer {
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .footer-col h4 { color: white; margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .footer-col ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        .footer-col li { margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .footer-col i { color: var(--gold); width: 20px; }
        
        .social-icons a { color: white; margin-right: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem; transition: 0.3s; }
        .social-icons a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

        /* Button Styles */
        .btn-cta {
            padding: 15px 50px; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; color: black;
            background: var(--gold); border-radius: 30px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block; transition: 0.3s; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .btn-cta:hover { background: white; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.5); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; padding: 30px 50px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box; z-index: 100;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-weight: bold; color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.8rem;">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> DineDock.
        </div>
        <div>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-bottom: 5px;">MY DASHBOARD</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 30px; font-weight: bold;">LOGIN</a>
                <a href="/login" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--gold); padding: 10px 25px; border-radius: 30px; font-weight: bold;">REGISTER</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-hero">
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 4.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; text-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
            Taste & Tranquility
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #ddd; font-weight: 300;">
            Nikmati hidangan kelas dunia tanpa kekhawatiran parkir. 
            Satu platform untuk reservasi meja dan slot kendaraan Anda secara real-time.
        </p>
        
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px;">
            <a href="/menu" class="btn-cta" style="background: transparent; border: 2px solid white; color: white;">View Menu</a>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-cta">Reserve Now</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="btn-cta">Reserve Now</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase">
        <div class="showcase-item">
            <img src="/img/restaurant.jpg" alt="Interior Restoran" class="showcase-img">
            <div class="showcase-text">
                <h3>Premium Dining</h3>
                <p>Interior modern dengan nuansa hangat, cocok untuk makan malam romantis maupun pertemuan bisnis. Tersedia 10 meja eksklusif dengan privasi terjaga.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="showcase-item">
            <img src="/img/parking.jpg" alt="Area Parkir" class="showcase-img">
            <div class="showcase-text">
                <h3>Secured Parking</h3>
                <p>Area parkir luas dengan sistem monitoring keamanan 24 jam. Terintegrasi langsung dengan reservasi meja Anda. Tidak perlu lagi berputar mencari slot kosong.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            
            <div class="footer-col" style="flex: 1.5;">
                <div style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-weight: bold; color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    DineDock.
                </div>
                <p>Sistem manajemen reservasi restoran dan parkir terintegrasi pertama di Indonesia. Memberikan kenyamanan dari pintu masuk hingga meja makan.</p>
                <div class="social-icons" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-col" style="flex: 1;">
                <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> 
                        <span>+62 812-3456-7890 (Reservasi)</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> 
                        <span>info@dinedock.com</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> 
                        <span>+62 812-9876-5432 (CS 24 Jam)</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-col" style="flex: 1;">
                <h4>Visit Us</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li style="align-items: flex-start;">
                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="margin-top: 5px;"></i>
                        <span>
                            Jl. Jenderal Sudirman No. 45<br>
                            Semarang, Jawa Tengah<br>
                            Indonesia 50229
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="far fa-clock"></i> 
                        <span>Open Daily: 10:00 - 22:00 WIB</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; border-top: 1px dashed #333; padding-top: 20px;">
            &copy; 2025 DineDock Integrated System. All Rights Reserved.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>